Critical iOS PWA rules:

- No localStorage — all state in JS vars or server-side
- Input font-size >= 16px
- padding-bottom: 30px on tab bar (home indicator)
- env(safe-area-inset-top) on toasts and header
- overscroll-behavior: contain on all scrollable areas
- Pull-to-refresh checks scroller.scrollTop, not window.scrollY
- Copy CSS from old dashboard — don’t reinvent it

